updater.crypto
Class RSAKey

java.lang.Object
  updater.crypto.RSAKey

public class RSAKey
extends java.lang.Object

The RSA key reader and writer.

This read and write the modulus and exponents in XML format.
Operations are not thread-safe.

Author:
Chan Wai Shing
